## 🔍 IF SOMETHING STILL DOESN'T WORK

### Error: "Cannot POST /api/auth/register"
```bash
# Make sure backend is running
npm start  # in backend folder
```

### Error: "Failed to load billing data"
```bash
# You might have old data. Clear it:
mongosh api-logging-db -e "db.dropDatabase()"
# Then restart backend
npm start
```

### Error: "Registration still failing"
```bash
# Check logs in backend terminal
# Should show: "User registered successfully"
# If not, backend might not have latest code

# Make sure you're in backend folder:
npm start  # This starts fresh
```

### Register button not clickable
```bash
# Make sure frontend is running:
npm start  # in frontend folder
```

